formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. At the time of registration of the project, all expenses of the project including On site Expenses  was included in the estimated  cost of Construciton as given in Point no. ii - a (i) of  CA Certificate (ie. Total Estimated cost of Construction and on site expenses is 6,03,85,270/-). Accordingly, the figure of total Cost of Construction incurred and paid as given in Point no. ii - a (ii) includes On site expenses incurred and paid.
2.  In Annexure to CA Certificate (Form 3A), in the column "Date of Agreement of Sale",  date of Agreement of sale or Date of Sale deed as applicable in particular case is provided.
3.  In Annexure to CA Certificate (Form 3A), some units are booked where payment more than 10% has been receive, however Agreement to sale has not been executed. The management have given explanation that, allottee has given written request to Promotor that allottee is not sure about in whose name document to be executed, so till the name is  finalized do not execute the agreement to sale.
4.  In Annexure to CA Certificate (Form 3A), in the column"Mobile Number of Allottee" as per request of promoters, contact number of Promotor is provided due to security reasons.
5. This certificate is issued based on provisional books of accounts as on 31st December, 2020 as provided to us by promotors.
